            "value": [
                "FUN LED CHARACTER NIGHT LIGHT: From Avengers and Despicable Me Minions, to Frozen 2 and Disney Princess, these adorable 120V LED bulb plug-in night lights will keep your little ones feeling safe and secure after dark; suitable for hallways, bathrooms, bedrooms and more with your kid’s favorite movie characters lighting the way",
